        <div class="gear-panels gear-ride">
            <h2>Our Ride Into the Wild</h2>

            <div class="para-item">
                <h3>
                    BMW X1 <span>– where the journey begins in comfort.</span>
                </h3>

                <p class="main-para">
                    Before the wild roads called for more, the BMW X1 was our
                    go-to companion — a smooth, comfortable ride that brought us
                    to the edge of adventure. It handled long drives and early
                    starts with grace, making every journey to the destination
                    effortless.<br /><br />
                    Even today, it holds its place in our story — a refined ride
                    for the open road, always ready when comfort and pace lead the
                    way.
                </p>
                <div class="two-img-panel">
                    <img
                        src="/images/gear/bmw-x1-1.webp"
                        alt="BMW X1"
                        class="singleImage"
                    />
                    <img
                        src="/images/gear/bmw-x1-2.webp"
                        alt="BMW X1"
                        class="singleImage"
                    />
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="para-item">
                <h3>
                    Prado J95 4x4 <span
                        >– where the road surrenders to nature.</span
                    >
                </h3>

                <p class="main-para">
                    When comfort met its limit, we turned to something built for
                    the wild. The Prado J95 became our trusted ride into the
                    unknown — powerful, durable, and ready for anything. It
                    climbs, crosses, and crawls through landscapes where tracks
                    fade and silence deepens.<br /><br />
                    From remote shoots to golden-hour escapes, this 4x4 carries more
                    than just gear. It moves with purpose — taking our vision deeper
                    into the untamed.
                </p>
                <div class="two-img-panel">
                    <img
                        src="/images/gear/prado-1.webp"
                        alt="Prado J95"
                        class="singleImage"
                    />
                    <img
                        src="/images/gear/prado-2.webp"
                        alt="Prado J95"
                        class="singleImage"
                    />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

